last_episode_to_air.name: Finale: The Monster
last_episode_to_air.overview: It all comes down to this. The top six drivers race through nine obstacles to determine the ultimate champion on four wheels.

name: Hyperdrive
overview: Elite street racers from around the world test their limits in supercharged custom cars on the biggest, baddest automotive obstacle course ever built.

episodes.name: Qualifier 1: Ready to Launch
episodes.overview: The amped-up drivers get their first experience on the course, but not everyone has what it takes to dominate behind the wheel.

episodes.name: Qualifier 2: Roll the Dice
episodes.overview: A millionaire with a Lamborghini, a truck driver in a stock Mustang and a slew of other racers in tricked-out rides push each other to new extremes

episodes.name: Qualifier 3: Enter the Assassin
episodes.overview: The qualifying rounds continue with the craziest obstacle yet and six new racers. The standout is a 21-year-old nicknamed the Baby-Faced Assassin.

episodes.name: Qualifier 4: Go Hard or Go Home
episodes.overview: The qualifying rounds continue with the craziest obstacle yet and six new racers. The standout is a 21-year-old nicknamed the Baby-Faced Assassin.

episodes.name: Knockout 1: Head to Head
episodes.overview: As the knockout round begins, the drivers must prove themselves on a newly redesigned course. But not everyone's car survives the chaos.

episodes.name: Knockout 2: Checkers or Wreckers
episodes.overview: A new obstacle humbles the racers -- even one indomitable driver. Another contestant's overconfidence proves costly on the track.

episodes.name: Knockout 3: Track Is Hot
episodes.overview: With the competition down to eight drivers, the track designers crank up the difficulty with a new obstacle that turns out to be alarmingly dangerous.

episodes.name: Wild Card: A Chance at Redemption
episodes.overview: A few old favorites return to the course for a series of head-to-head battles. The prize: a second chance at glory.

episodes.name: Semifinal: Last Chance
episodes.overview: The course is downright diabolical. The margin for error is thinner than ever. The finale is nearly here. Go, drivers, go!

episodes.name: Finale: The Monster
episodes.overview: It all comes down to this. The top six drivers race through nine obstacles to determine the ultimate champion on four wheels.
